{"type": "article", "id": 39662, "title": "拿着笔就不自觉有小动作？这个设计满足你｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-04-10T23:20:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 5438, "name": "Dolce & Gabbana"}, {"id": 23124, "name": "SMEG"}, {"id": 39376, "name": "Duncan Shotton"}, {"id": 39377, "name": "Marc Ange"}, {"id": 39378, "name": "Jeroen van Kesteren"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 14, "praise_count": 211, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170410211656yGrF3KZ41TEhnXM9.jpeg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Fidgi Pen</h3><p>如果你也时常因为焦虑而忍不住把玩什么东西或是做一些小动作的话，由美国设计团队带来的 Fidgi Pen 可以让你玩得更隐蔽一些。轻按、旋转、滑动等常见的抗焦虑功能都被集合进了这支笔中，由于摆脱了市面上同类产品所标榜的“玩具”标签，你也不用担心在办公场合被人发现“不务正业”了。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/fidgipen/fidgi-pen-a-fidget-toy-disguised-as-a-pen\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 24 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410211817bfiZ4uQWeTxEwsj7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667647\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410211818EB5WfMgO8Y24a0Th.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.558824\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410211819rSiA98pu4NZwUmD2.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704102118195o6BMaxqWnYs3P9e.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.566176\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410211817Q4IBnfvMxrwUKq0W.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410211817Pu7pVzO9rIX1eo4R.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tobiishi by Duncan Shotton</h3><p>对一部分日本的居民来说，迎客开门意味着他们得在换上户外鞋和伸长手臂够门把手这两个动作间做出选择。为此，现居东京的英国设计师 <a href=\"http://dshott.co.uk/\">Duncan Shotton</a> 以日式花园中常见的石阶为原型，推出了这款名为 Tobiishi 的踏脚垫，让选择后者的人不再担心自己会失去平衡摔在玄关地上。这是它的<a href=\"http://dshott.co.uk/product/tobiishi/\">购买链接</a>，售价为 14.95 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410211926jNXMgU42xD8ya5ui.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410211926DUf5iVq74Mlcstpv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410211928lQwJpexarMcf0mk4.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410211929Lyg5aBEui0TojKPN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Le Refuge by Marc Ange</h3><p>每一个设计活动都会有一件在 Instagram 上出镜率极高的作品，在今年的米兰设计周上，由现居巴黎的意大利设计师 <a href=\"http://www.bloomroomstudio.com/\">Marc Ange</a> 带来的 Le Refuge 就吸引了不少人为它按下快门。Ange 在巨大的木制底座上摆放了一张粉色的床铺，并围绕它布置了巨型的粉色树叶，营造出一个很适合做白日梦的奇特空间。如果你身在米兰，可以在 Wallpaper* Handmade 的展区找到它。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212000C4NpvHm1croVYZbl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212000xchgryK4AT3OnUJe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410211959RukoTFbAUNjW1n5H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410211959dpu4hJePXRHjKmUG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017041021195907hKewUYPXMdQBG8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sicily is my Love by Dolce &amp; Gabbana and Smeg</h3><p>还记得奢侈品牌 Dolce &amp; Gabbana 和意大利家电制造商 <a href=\"http://www.smegusa.com/\">Smeg</a> 以 Made in Italy 为主题推出的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/26239.html\">华丽冰箱</a>吗？今年他们再度合作，在这套名为 Sicily is my Love 的系列中，让更多家电穿上了西西里岛艺术风格的外衣，明亮的配色加上各类具有当地特色的图案为原本冰冷的电器增添了一种仿佛置身盛夏海岸的活力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212033cQe3UXov5Z0BkVji.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.296000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212033og0RSrHWEa42hiUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751880\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212033Hndkehp8AbziWrc4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212034sLPSF1qKdOG4x8UH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212034FUIKE7yd6vwkOi2X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Well by Matter &amp; Mindtribe</h3><p>美国旧金山的工业设计公司 <a href=\"http://matterglobal.com/\">Matter</a> 最近和工程公司 Mindtribe 合作推出了一个名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/50245405/Well\">Well</a> 的家用节水系统，利用硬件和智能软件间的协作让住户能够即时了解家中的用水情况。在发现淋浴时浪费的水占据了很大比重之后，他们决定先对常见的浴室花洒进行改造：像勺子一样的支架取代了常见的环状结构，花洒的背面则借助磁力吸附在其中，让用户可以更灵活地调整出水角度。目前，Well 还处于概念设计阶段，尚未投入生产。</p><p><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212336NyaUfLSEgxTkRuvD.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212336I5DGM4KywBV9Y01R.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212335OWFLEHX2n7IV1gky.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212335NlKEcZTkXp5PV3az.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563032\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Orphanage for Lost Adventures by Jeroen van Kesteren</h3><p>和蒸汽朋克有关的作品不一定非得围绕皮革和金属，这套名为 Orphanage for Lost Adventures 的飞行器模型就是荷兰艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.invorm.com/\">Jeroen van Kesteren</a> 利用纸板、铝箔、纸张和粘合剂打造的。考虑到材质本身的脆弱和对细节的考究，每一个飞行器都要耗费 Jeroen 一个月左右的时间完成，高度在 40 到 50 厘米左右。如果你感兴趣的话，可以在他的 <a href=\"https://nl.pinterest.com/jeevankee/orphanage-for-lost-adventures/\">Pinterest</a> 上看到完整的系列。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212128kz5QLx8hJcsWOE3v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212128dJvBC7GFmSYgX1yb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212128SKcV9Phk60WL4e3N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017041021212869JMRsp3WaeVHytb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170410212128ieW2trXYRn8QdAuL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}